- simpleini <https://github.com/brofield/simpleini>
- sqlite_modern_cpp <https://github.com/SqliteModernCpp/sqlite_modern_cpp>
- Thor <https://github.com/Bromeon/Thor>
- {fmt} <https://fmt.dev/latest/index.html>
- Backward-cpp <https://github.com/bombela/backward-cpp>

Please note the author of Sorcery: Shadows under Llylgamyn, gives additional
permission under the GNU GPL version 3 section 7 to link all source code released
as part of Sorcery, to these libraries (as per the declaration in each source file.

